snippet.title: Wipeout in the Zone - Official Trailer (Xbox 360)
snippet.description:
Wipeout In The Zone will be Kinect ready for the Xbox 360 and available this summer in conjunction with the premier of Wipeout's summer season on ABC.

Read more about the game: http://www.gamespot.com/624571
